parameters:
Tourist: I came to visit the temple,
it's a magnificent building, isn't it?

Tourist: I never thought angels could be
such terrifying beings...

Tourist: I should have worshipped the
Demon Lord after all...

Tourist: I wonder if I'll be attacked by
an angel on my way back... Ugh... I hope
I'll be okay...

Tourist: Huh? Did you enter the wrong
room, miss?

Tourist: I came here for sightseeing
with my grandchild, but I wonder if we
can enjoy seeing the temple?

Tourist: I came for sightseeing at the
worst possible timing...

Tourist: We don't have time for
sightseeing anymore, so we're planning
to leave too.

Tourist: If you don't want to be thrown
into prison, get out of here quickly.

Swordsman: I stopped by on my journey,
but I sense an ominous presence from the
temple priests.
The swordsman: I was about to be killed by an angel, but the old lady in the next room saved me.

Swordsman: She was a master of martial
arts.

Swordsman: I took in the old lady next
door as my disciple. We're planning to
leave Logres together.

Swordsman: W-What?! Naked!? Put on some
clothes, clothes!!
